    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d think it just arrived from the factory today! I\u2019ve treated this car like my own baby\u2014it\u2019s been pampered, kept spotless, and runs like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
