    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment by its sole owner. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases or wear, while the original floor mats look untouched. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, switch, and electronic system functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly flawless machine that looks, feels, and drives like new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
